•   Open a new SAS program file using the multi-point button or press the F4 key on your keyboard.  
•   Paste the following program into the program file.  
```sas
proc glmselect data=diabetes plots=coefficients;
model Y = Age Gender BMI BP Total_Cholesterol LDL HDL TCH LTG Glucose                  /selection = elasticnet(choose=AICC);
partition fraction(validate=0.3); /* Optional: Split data for validation */
run;
```
•   The "/selection" option specifies the penalization method used. In this case, we use Elastic Net (弹性网络 (Elastic NET)). This method can be changed to LASSO or Ridge Regression (岭回归 (Ridge)).
